{"tid":1144280,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"早晨","createTime":"2019-05-08T03:59:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T14:29:16.000Z","uid":41859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3bfb7b3df490195fe256f1332c0edf9dbc6018f1","tid":1144280,"uid":41859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:59:57.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"b5f37307017ce8367c9fba681ac1e3df52d68e11","tid":1144280,"uid":113373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:01:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰<br />\n<br />\n星期六 早上8點半 <br />\n立法會將會開會討論有關修訂 暫未知會否表決 <br />\n由於秘書處政變 原本由涂謹申主持會議改為石禮謙主持<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人任何罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</strong></span>"},{"pid":"41c65267ca24777a193d8d7c545e4cb5eb882f6a","tid":1144280,"uid":173317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:03:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4714a6abb14b1b864fa7613155995e2a15c8da2f","tid":1144280,"uid":41859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:04:51.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41519d669ce826a611f22f53258d1406669d59c","tid":1144280,"uid":188297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:07:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d4997320c368e230fa58764b0a07cdda7ea3cd4","tid":1144280,"uid":41859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d41519d669ce826a611f22f53258d1406669d59c","tid":1144280,"uid":188297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4714a6abb14b1b864fa7613155995e2a15c8da2f","tid":1144280,"uid":4